  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c2d769a3-6688-45b1-b235-dcc5331e3d5d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3844f2fd-480c-4a9f-a2d5-ada927dda52e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b9d126da-e882-4de2-9c26-fe2245468303\"><b>안녕하세요</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c1191399-c78b-481e-884a-1df4b45e80ad\"><b> </b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e154b401-de0f-4fac-bb95-933b7107e974\"><b>이수한의원입니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-c2d769a3-6688-45b1-b235-dcc5331e3d5d\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0a79ad12-0e9c-4ec7-8217-e2ff6f399288\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n                                <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" data-linkdata='{\"src\" : \"\", \"packCode\" : \"motion2d_01\", \"seq\" : \"10\", \"width\" : \"\", \"height\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/motion2d_01/original_10.png?type=p100_100\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" />\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-065886dc-cc83-495e-bd6c-cd96de913a7d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-aa5d6d85-ad39-4eb8-8535-206e9ecef199\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a7676fea-ca60-47e3-ac8f-7dcf285ff8c7\">혹시 이유 없이 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c6733932-429a-47c3-9e9b-cffc8f7fab03\"><b>온몸이 뻐근하고, 근육통이 지속</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b569c33b-1670-4219-976f-583d36c349e4\">되어 힘드신가요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a447d9d5-70ef-46d8-85c9-767bebf2b3c4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-afa4f843-220d-4705-9fe1-60d55d359f0e\">섬유근육통은 특별한 외상 없이도 근육과 인대, 관절 부위에 통증이 반복되는 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-23519f65-fb23-4d8e-a6f0-4085697772b1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4ce3a060-7157-4c0a-b095-11e3a3201017\">만성 질환입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7fca5279-1667-44e8-8838-d6e43beea4b1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a83d0d7e-b00d-4816-92f9-a1575df15fd2\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4c1f94cf-1ec2-4a35-b010-b4671e24c7a0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-33da445f-1931-4ba4-a96a-f2eb22f342c8\">단순 피로와는 달리, 일상생활까지 방해할 정도로 통증이 이어지기 때문에 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5a24382e-dbc3-45fa-9d90-eaf0849e7349\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2986fd56-8028-441a-973a-5d89bee08585\">조기 관리가 중요합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8d4529eb-526a-4b01-8fa1-e86ea8baa7c9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9cb89de4-9600-4231-952c-6f2e42f46b95\">오늘은 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-45dfdc78-3243-48b0-9075-fbd572d83ccc\"><b>한방 관점에서 섬유근육통을 완화하는 방법</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9e1c6bf1-9e6f-4d5c-954e-56a68efd06c4\">과 함께,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a7c77bb7-15ab-45b3-af70-8301026b8010\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3485ecfa-c25d-4249-9ec6-994e9aaab944\">통증을 줄이는 생활 습관을 소개해드리겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-065886dc-cc83-495e-bd6c-cd96de913a7d\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-38dd8e77-ce2f-4f56-8aec-43434d7bdfa8\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-16fc2c6e-b287-443e-a27d-934dba66ff3d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-16fc2c6e-b287-443e-a27d-934dba66ff3d\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/259353d53ba09bdb.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1600\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1600\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\" }'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/259353d53ba09bdb.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/259353d53ba09bdb.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-16fc2c6e-b287-443e-a27d-934dba66ff3d\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_postit\" id=\"SE-257cfa76-35d8-4ca7-9968-1b80908ee640\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_postit\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b3f6d030-4a59-4232-986a-d2125f3e6ff6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-86d86209-f9c6-475f-a061-926cd3614fa7\"><b>섬유근육통의 원인과 특징</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f3040aed-1ce4-471a-b9e7-440144638d00\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0b257053-e76f-4483-9aab-91883903fa42\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bd25f9e6-1d28-42a7-9e94-0e742a9cabca\">섬유근육통은 서양의학적으로는 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-19d82b47-73dd-4246-9953-54eadf7187b3\"><b>중추신경계의 통증 조절 이상, 스트레스, </b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ba12ff91-02ce-487b-b909-748539213eae\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-dc808c94-9ccd-4f5a-9274-57a81200eee3\"><b>수면 장애</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6b542093-45c0-4137-aef7-ebb9fc879573\"> 등이 원인으로 알려져 있습니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-28e6f7ca-8eb2-4763-b367-f2ac1da17cf3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-cdd8e05c-0c26-4367-9da5-32a28be10195\">한의학에서는 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b982ae6d-ff71-47a0-a662-9f7b77453e82\"><b>기혈의 순환 장애</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9114bc43-81f3-4553-bfa5-495d6f697c4e\">와 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d74f86c8-05be-445e-82bb-714de8dfb0f8\"><b>간·신의 기능 저하</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4a9c3565-99d5-4a67-b55f-71922f07475f\">가 통증의 근본 원인으로 해석됩니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bf86858e-d6a7-43c1-92fd-39b02b09839e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c050bbfb-e0cc-4177-9bc0-e4bb510091ee\">특징적으로</span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a0d9e541-d09c-4c34-87a1-7250df3ceaf5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5fe7d26c-ca43-413e-be19-568c81549456\">전신 18개 압통점 부위에서 통증이 발생</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d151f900-5cc0-44aa-9bf7-5b7b65c98c01\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-68f39117-d28d-4b77-8ce8-e0b7ca3b989a\">피로감, 수면장애, 기억력 저하, 우울감 등이 동반 되는 경우가 많습니다.</span></p></li></ul><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-f3040aed-1ce4-471a-b9e7-440144638d00\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-32e411cb-b994-4c8f-8757-8a9c66c0680d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-b8eb287f-9d48-4d84-9e0a-6a1e089b7a43\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-31848032-a54e-4ec1-a9d0-8deb0b831f16\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6cdcdf56-0863-4385-9121-b557fb64ad13\"><b>한방 치료 접근법 – 기혈 순환 촉진</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-47fedd9c-5965-4139-a69d-c167965ba992\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ed0306b6-6ccc-41f1-836c-ddcf666e895f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-aa2f85d5-5f33-4ecb-bcf1-addef01b50ce\">한의학에서는 통증을 “막힌 기혈이 제대로 돌지 못해 생긴 결과”로 봅니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ceaaaa56-dfe9-4c46-85b3-46b0218153d1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87a14b9d-0651-4e33-a94b-71b7e2d50e55\">따라서 치료는 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f43bcf2a-4356-44f8-a1e3-cee1ebc8b991\"><b>기혈 순환을 원활히 하여 통증을 완화</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0f54386e-0aac-4f1b-a2fc-ab2df18bf989\">하는 데 초점이 맞춰집니다.</span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1a2f1e91-736a-4001-bd8b-b63f5c4f4b66\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-885978dd-f773-4d37-bedb-b9127c1dba99\"><b>한약</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9e3ad6da-78cf-48e5-b1b8-97bf78d9fbd3\">: 간·신 기능을 보강하고, 기혈을 보충하는 처방 사용</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0b760147-f069-46c8-ace9-6b99c1bbfea0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3ae629b1-8a69-4465-9abd-f79b5474bb8c\"><b>침 치료</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-171d39cd-723a-467b-b7f5-fab8ed50c0c4\">: 경락의 순환을 열어주어 근육 긴장을 풀어줌</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8d253e3e-c792-49b7-bd4c-1759bb1aab93\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-dd9fdbef-cfa3-4693-98f5-bc9a2c5125de\"><b>뜸·부항</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5a6968a8-fd5c-4095-a7ed-1f9c0d44df4a\">: 혈류 개선 및 근육 뭉침 완화에 도움</span></p></li></ul><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-47fedd9c-5965-4139-a69d-c167965ba992\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-9cdf4ad4-9e56-4dc6-a676-e7b974204596\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-b7b401f6-be29-4b76-b635-d156b9be86f0\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-81f33392-e40c-42a3-b2cb-8351e9a14959\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-fbbf6bc3-6964-46bb-b2f4-1b82cbf26129\"><b>스트레스와 식습관 관리</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-aeb48698-d31d-4cf4-986a-4999f833c2ea\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9cbc9b6a-72a3-477e-a83a-745b193b7456\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b0bf061c-34c2-46c5-87d9-dddfe08e51ef\">섬유근육통 환자분들은 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-fa4dc5be-2e52-494f-83c0-6ebcc4eb6851\"><b>스트레스에 민감하게 반응</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8a194048-91eb-467b-b6ae-3d28704df5c8\">하는 경우가 많습니다.</span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3e59ae04-3cbb-4413-a753-cd47862955ec\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0d8a1276-4c47-4fc5-9c53-43fbf73b3dbd\">규칙적인 식사와 과로 방지</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7408de54-1e1b-403c-a950-083091dce39e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-156195b5-4a15-4c24-9eeb-6e420480a6b8\">카페인·가공식품 줄이기</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0ffe5999-c73d-4d47-b646-09a6bb84deda\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-43c527ea-f821-40b7-a6e0-65f951edeabb\">오메가-3, 비타민 D가 풍부한 음식 섭취</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fb265c78-f960-4355-b3f0-1d97ff0dae97\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8dbf73f8-80b1-47fe-a1ef-59bdec43289d\">이러한 식습관은 몸의 염증 반응을 낮추고 회복력을 돕습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-aeb48698-d31d-4cf4-986a-4999f833c2ea\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-7389f359-5f47-494e-842a-99277c076667\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-af045f01-4315-47b2-82b7-e3dc1f168d53\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-590d043a-2d1f-49c3-ab60-547b0e0f6258\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d0c9acbe-4d86-4014-8e24-a5cbba7d2373\"><b>효과적인 운동과 생활 습관</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8bedb1e1-4b6b-4369-832f-75d4bd3c10f4\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4f5ec7b0-7b83-4b0b-8451-8fa0c2a7eb17\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7c26b2c2-df61-4697-b547-96cad293bac1\">통증이 있다고 무조건 쉬는 것은 오히려 근육을 약화시켜 증상을 악화시킬 수 있습니다.</span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9f9c3e6e-00a3-46c2-b022-deccaf8abf73\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c96ce6eb-3dcc-4be3-8afc-6b619056e6f4\"><b>가벼운 유산소 운동</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e14f775e-021c-415a-ac5f-550785071f09\">: 걷기, 수영, 자전거 타기</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1c496f6c-716e-43f3-a3a3-bf61b1de7f64\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e00a6e59-d284-4911-a3ca-7cd26cc3fbcd\"><b>스트레칭</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-985ce38c-10cd-449e-9826-f37709fc5835\">: 근육 긴장 완화</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7a6b50d8-3af9-46c3-88a4-9d6dde107867\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b4cd2f94-88bd-4aba-96ad-b27248af45da\"><b>수면 관리</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2777172f-6c77-4395-82a9-46c0740a2516\">: 일정한 수면 리듬 유지</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4be09ed2-3b47-4dc0-8ad1-205af24b2ce0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f0ea72d0-9393-4b68-8766-a3b061eb8414\">규칙적인 생활습관은 신체뿐 아니라 마음의 안정에도 큰 도움이 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-8bedb1e1-4b6b-4369-832f-75d4bd3c10f4\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-5b288774-4be3-4c12-bef3-b26545d223e5\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-278c10dd-b1c6-44e2-8d64-7522976a657a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1742348f-c1dd-4190-847e-85cd97e8b5de\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-920d528f-0842-4eb4-adbf-d1e2bfcc0959\"><b>참지 말고, 관리하세요</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ebecc38f-9b24-4fe1-96f0-67b35ff9766f\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-78664b3a-c88f-4368-af9e-95c784a8f7aa\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87318446-f3d5-4c36-97a8-95783e843424\">섬유근육통은 단순히 “피곤해서 생기는 통증”이 아닙니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3643498b-c11b-42c2-bfd8-ce70dd1dbfff\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d8921ba6-909a-49c3-a10e-ed81d11fdaad\"><b>기혈 순환 관리, 스트레스 조절, 올바른 운동과 식습관</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-24bed2da-f92a-44c6-b7ef-0cf7f709cd2d\">을 함께 실천한다면, 통증은 충분히 완화할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-ebecc38f-9b24-4fe1-96f0-67b35ff9766f\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b4776271-931e-4428-9d5e-d3b9054418e7\">\n                    <div class=